body.name: MIYOCAR Custom Baby Formula Dispenser with Scoop and Leveller Portable Storage baby milk powder Containers for Travel, Non-Spill Smart Baby Food Storage Container for Fruits, Snacks and Nuts
features: MILK POWDER DISPENSER: The formula container is made of high food-grade PP plastic that is BPA-free, environmentally friendly, suitable for moist- heat and freezer safe as well.
KEEPS THE FOOD FRESH AND SAFE: This dispenser has a buckle design and silicone sealing ring inner lid ensuring food is fresh and preventing formula from getting wet and from any damage.

Multiple Compartments: A milk powder dispenser is a great way to store your formula. It has multiple compartments so you can keep the spoon separate from the formula. This reduces the risk of cross-contamination. The leveller design helps you scoop out each spoonful of formula precisely without wasting.

WIDELY APPLICABLE: This dispenser is easy to use, just be ready to feed, add the powder into the feeding bottle of pre-boiled water, shake it and feed your baby. The container also works as a fruit storage container, snack cup for cookies and other similar items.
GREAT GIFT --Can personalize with baby name or photo, Ideal Gift for Baby Showers, Christenings, Gender Reveal, Parties, and more!Unique gift to the little ones
